# Adamovo, Republic of Buryatia

}}
Adamovo () is a rural locality (a selo) in Barguzinsky District, Republic of Buryatia, Russia. The population was 185 as of 2010. There are 4 streets.
Geography
Adamovo is located 29&nbsp;km southwest of Barguzin (the district's administrative centre) by road. Zorino is the nearest rural locality.
